OL,3,CMotorcyclist killed in crash in Leeds
OL,5,FA 22-year-old motorcyclist has been
OL,6,Fkilled following a collision with a
OL,7,Fcar on Hawkhill Avenue.
OL,9,FOfficers were called at just after 4pm
OL,10,Fon Friday, 19 June, to Cross Gates
OL,11,FRoad when a BYD Atto and a Honda
OL,12,Fmotorbike were in collision crossing
OL,13,FCross Gates Road at the junction of
OL,14,FHawkhill Avenue.
OL,16,FThe rider of the motorcycle a 22-year-
OL,17,Fold man died in hospital
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
